        <updateDate>2021-09-14T15:30:41Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>National Firearms Amendments Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill includes within the definition of <i>firearm</i> under the National Firearms Act a semiautomatic rifle or shotgun that has the capacity to accept a detachable ammunition feeding device.</p>]]>
        </text>
